HEADWORD: Pellucidness
<hw>Pel*lu"cid*ness</hw>
<pr>(?)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>pellucid</ets>itas.]</ety> <def>The quality or state of being
